		<title>12EMPLOYMENT</title>
		<content>   Being a farming community the main  
 source of employment in the area is   
 based on the land. There is little    
 unemployment as much of the housing is
 tied to the job.                      
   Most of the people living in Belsay 
 village are{retired,}having worked on 
 the{farms}or on the{Belsay Estate.}The
 younger/newer residents commute to    
 work in{Newcastle or Morpeth.         
   The opening of{Belsay Hall}and      
{Castle}in 1984 has created a few jobs 
 but in the main these are not filled  
 by local people.                      
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
